        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: November 2, 2025</p>
        
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Mining Toolkit ("App," "we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use the Mining Toolkit iOS application.</p>
        
        <h2>Data Collection</h2>
        <p><strong>Mining Toolkit does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information.</strong></p>
        
        <p>The App operates entirely on your device. All calculations, data entry, and reference materials are processed and stored locally on your device only. We do not:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Collect your name, email, phone number, or other personal identifiers</li>
            <li>Collect location data or device information</li>
            <li>Create or maintain user accounts</li>
            <li>Transmit data to external servers or third parties</li>
            <li>Use analytics or tracking tools</li>
            <li>Sell or share your data</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How Your Data is Protected</h2>
        <p>Since all data remains on your device:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your data is protected by your device's built-in security features</li>
            <li>No third parties have access to your calculations or inputs</li>
            <li>Deleting the App removes all associated data from your device</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Mining Toolkit does not integrate with third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. The App is completely self-contained.</p>
        
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Mining Toolkit does not knowingly collect information from children under 13. The App is designed for professional and educational use and is appropriate for users of all ages due to its non-invasive nature.</p>
        
        <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected with an updated "Last Updated" date at the top of this page.</p>
        
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or the Mining Toolkit App, please contact us:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> jory.dion@gmail.com</p>
        
